HOUSE BILL 2418
By Boyd
SENATE BILL 2593
By Johnson
AN ACT to amend Tennessee Code Annotated, Title 4;
Title 5; Title 6; Title 7; Title 9; Title 12; Title 13;
Title 48; Title 50; Title 64; Title 65 and Title 67,
relative to boards of utilities.
BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF THE STATE OF TENNESSEE:
SECTION 1. Tennessee Code Annotated, Section 7-36-110(c), is amended by deleting
"ninety (90) days" and substituting "ninety-five (95) days".
SECTION 2. This act takes effect upon becoming a law, the public welfare requiring it.
